<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><% .Name %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/workshop.css">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #1e1e2e;
      color: #cdd6f4;
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    nav {
      width: 260px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #181825;
      border-right: 1px solid #313244;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #cba6f7;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #313244;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-section { padding: 1rem 0; }
    .nav-label {
      padding: 0.35rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #6c7086;
    }
    a.gdoc-nav__entry {
      display: block;
      padding: 0.45rem 1.5rem;
      color: #bac2de;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-left: 3px solid transparent;
      transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    }
    a.gdoc-nav__entry:hover { color: #cdd6f4; background: #313244; }
    a.gdoc-nav__entry.active {
      color: #cba6f7;
      border-left-color: #cba6f7;
      background: rgba(203, 166, 247, 0.08);
    }
    main { flex: 1; padding: 3rem 4rem; max-width: 860px; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #cba6f7; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #89b4fa; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.7; color: #bac2de; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    code {
      background: #313244;
      color: #f5c2e7;
      padding: 0.15em 0.45em;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
      font-size: 0.88em;
    }
    pre {
      background: #181825;
      border: 1px solid #313244;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    pre code { background: none; padding: 0; color: #cdd6f4; font-size: 0.87rem; }
    .hero {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      background: #181825;
      border: 1px solid #313244;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-emoji { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .hero p { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
      background: #cba6f7;
      color: #1e1e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #d0b4f8; }
    .chapter-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .chapter-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: #181825;
      border: 1px solid #313244;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .chapter-list li a { color: #89b4fa; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .chapter-list li a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .chapter-num {
      background: #313244;
      color: #cba6f7;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: monospace;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a class="nav-logo" href="/">⚙ <% .Name %></a>
    <div class="nav-section">
      <div class="nav-label">Chapters</div>
      <a class="gdoc-nav__entry active" href="/00-setup/">00 — Setup</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <main>
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-emoji">⚙️</div>
      <h1><% .Name %></h1>
      <p>Welcome to the workshop! Complete each chapter and run <code>./<% .Slug %> check</code> to unlock the next one.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="/00-setup/">Start Chapter 00 →</a>
    </div>

    <h2>Chapters</h2>
    <ul class="chapter-list">
      <li>
        <span class="chapter-num">00</span>
        <div>
          <a href="/00-setup/">Setup</a>
          <p style="margin:0;font-size:0.85rem;color:#6c7086">Complete the initial setup steps.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>Each chapter has a set of automated checks. Run <code>./<% .Slug %> check</code> to validate your
    work and unlock the next chapter. The sidebar icons update live in the browser.</p>
    <pre><code>./<% .Slug %> check      # run checks for the current chapter
./<% .Slug %> status     # show all chapters
./<% .Slug %> reset      # reset progress</code></pre>
  </main>
  <script src="/workshop-progress.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
